column5: oh, well good luck! hope it gets better for you (:
thank you! good luck to you as well :D
thanks! i sometimes feel nauseous when i eat, especially in the morning, though i’m not sure why. i’m glad you fought through it :D
Thats great! don’t know what time it is where you are, but for me it’s morning, so good morning and good luck (:
ahah it’s 2am where i live B)

i’m proud of you for those weeks you were clean! you were strong, and you still are. you must feel awfull but i belive you can do this, you did it once, you can do it again! stay strong i care about you even if you’re a stranger on the internet (:
